## 📡 Communication Protocols

| Protocol | Direction | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| UART | NodeMCU TX → FPGA RX | Real-time health status transfer |
| MQTT | NodeMCU → Cloud Broker | Remote telemetry and diagnostics |

> **UART note:** NodeMCU `TX` is connected to the FPGA's `RX` pin. Ensure 3.3V logic level compatibility.

---

## 🌐 Cloud Integration (MQTT)

- **Protocol:** MQTT
- **Broker:** Configurable — Mosquitto / HiveMQ / AWS IoT Core
- **Suggested topic structure:**

```
relay/monitor/temperature
relay/monitor/status
relay/monitor/relay_state
```

- **Payload format (JSON):**

```json
{
  "temperature_c": 43.2,
  "relay_status": "ON",
  "health": "WARNING",
  "timestamp": 1713820800
}
```

**Enables:**
- Real-time temperature and relay status monitoring
- Remote diagnostics without physical access
- Scalable to multi-sensor / multi-relay systems
- Compatible with Node-RED, Grafana, or custom dashboards

