## 🧩 FPGA Verilog Modules

| Module | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `top.v` | Top-level integration of all submodules |
| `clk_divider.v` | Clock synthesis — divides system clock for relay timing |
| `relay_ctrl.v` | Relay state machine — handles UART input and push button |
| `uart_rx.v` | UART receiver — reads status byte from NodeMCU |

**Relay switching is triggered by:**
1. Internal clock logic (automatic timed switching via clock synthesis)
2. Push button on FPGA board (manual override)
3. UART command byte received from NodeMCU

