## 🛡️ Relay Driver & Protection Circuit

```
FPGA GPIO Pin
      │
    [220Ω] ── Base
                │
           BC546 NPN Transistor
                │ Collector
                │
          Optocoupler Input LED
          (inside relay module)
                │
          Optocoupler Output
                │
          Relay Coil (12V)
                │
          Switched Load
```

> A **flyback diode** across the relay coil terminals is recommended for additional spike suppression.

